text: Marta Estévez García (born 5 June 1997) is a Luxembourgish footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Luxembourg women's national team. She is of Spanish descent. ==Career== Estévez García has been capped for the Luxembourg national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Luxembourgian women's footballers Category:Luxembourgian people of Spanish descent Category:Luxembourg women's international footballers
